cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.RO 

This paper is about improving the performance of Reinforcement Learning (RL) by combining attention and agency features. RL is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also deals with state representations derived from pixel images (cs.CV) and proposes different architectures for RL (cs.NE, cs.RO).
